鋳ﾙ@fa43b42c45ad6ec0ef0746ad16cf6a318af4d92b8440672cb665d4516320f15dﾚ卦itle: This week in Nushell #255
Path: Nushell
Content:
devyn landed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13330] a massive Internal Representation (IR) compiler and evaluator PR 脂脂脂
 and then did lots of mostly related work: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13367] fixed the file count in the 
``Debug``
 implementation of 
``IrBlock``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13356] fixed the order of I/O types in 
``take until``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13355] included the actual output type in an OutputMismatch error
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13351] made the 
``store-env``
 IR instruction also update the config
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13345] added IR support to the debugger
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13343] included more argument types to 
``view ir``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13342] fixed the signature of 
``view ir``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13339] set the capacity of the Vec used in 
``gather_captures()``
 to the expected number of captures
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13338] avoided cloning in 
``Signature::get_positional()``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13334] made pipe redirections consistent and added 
``err>|``
 and similar forms
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13333] used Arc for environment variables on the stack
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13332] updated the config directly at assignment
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13310] made 
``into bits``
 produce a bitstring stream
.
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13371] prevented the 
``touch``
 command from being added twice to the default context
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13363] tweaked 
``parse``
 usage and examples for better clarity
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13340] did a quick fix up for IR PR as referenced
.
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13361] fixed 
``select``
 cell path renaming behavior
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13360] used conventional generic bounds
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13346] grouped dependabot updates for uutils/coreutils
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13344] bumped the yanked 
``libc``
 version
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12906] documented public types in 
``nu-protocol``
.
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13358] edited path form doc comments
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13329] continued the path migration with 
``nu-test-support``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13314] added and used a new 
``Signals``
 struct
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13309] started the path migration
.
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13353] fixed unused space issues when truncation is used and header on border is configured
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13325] fixed the kv table width issue with header_on_border configuration
.
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13337] fixed the main binary being rebuilt when nothing has changed
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13335] made 
``polars unpivot``
 consistent with 
``polars pivot``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13282] implemented a command to expose polars' pivot functionality
.
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13323] raised an error when using the invalid 
``o>|``
 pipe
.
ito-hiroki 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13315] fixed 
``from toml``
 to handle TOML datetime correctly
.
rgwood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13312] updated the 
``explore``
 feature to pass config to views at creation time
.
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13273] upgraded Ubuntu runners to 22.04 to fix nightly build errors
.
YizhePKU 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13024] fixed PWD-aware command hints
.
壷@52788e60e5928e34ffc7dfc700a88e01b3a01cf6174af2ae4443069387fa9a96ﾚ裕itle: This week in Nushell #255
Path: Nu_Scripts
Content:
cdfq152313 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/893] fixed an issue where SSH config might not contain a hostname
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/891] added SSH completion
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/892] added a Fibonacci benchmark for fairly low-level evaluation performance
.
